description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Anurak purrs with a rating of 54, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 270, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Box for East, Leverage for South, and 1 for West. Anurak has the personality suit of hodler. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/20545-94613-2.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Anurak [270 Votes, Hall of Fame]
